defaultQ28 Mark defaultHendrickdefault:default Can we view what is going on in 
defaultSyria
default in terms of a Sunni-
defaultShi’a
default conflict? Obviously the borders were drawn up many years ago, mainly as a result of colonialism, and they probably bear very little resemblance to genuine communities. Will 
defaultSyria
