defaultShashank Joshi:default No, I am not sure that is the case. It wouldn’t hurt of course. Both of the branches of al-Qaeda in 
defaultSyria
default are sort of offshoots of al-Qaeda’s branch in 
defaultIraq
default—both 
defaultISIS
default and 
defaultJabhat
default al-
defaultNusra
