default              
defaultQ54 Chair:default For our third and final session of the day, I welcome 
defaultShiraz Maher, Senior Fellow, International Centre for the Study of Radicalisation, King
default’
defaults College London
default, and Dr Rim 
defaultTurkmani
default, Director of 
defaultMadani
